textContent:
---lucky 7---

Happy 7th (9th XD) month together my baby!!! How time flies so fast! Dati shy type pa aq, pero now g na g na yung bby yagit mo HAHAHAHA

It's funny though, na we've only known each other for 9 months pero it really feels na I've known you all my life. We really are meant to stay together forever bby! I was made for loving you!

We've spent almost the whole week together, and I'm just so thankful and lucky na in the future, we get to see each other every day. Thank you bby for always being my battery, my stress reliever, my comfort person, and most importantly, my beloved bby boonion! This week was very stressful and I'm very lucky because you were always there to comfort me and support me during my hard moments. I'll do my best to repay the favor! Wag ka magsasawa sakin oki? I love you so much!! Happy monthsary ulit!! See you tomorrowww
